      public List<Photo.Tag> getTags()
      An array containing the users and their positions in this photo. The x and y coordinates are percentages from the left and top edges of the photo, respectively.
      Returns:
      An array containing the users and their positions in this photo. The x and y coordinates are percentages from the left and top edges of the photo, respectively.
